://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Dimension_Door\">Dimension Door</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Growth of Plants\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Growth_of_Plants\">Growth of Plants</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Hallucinatory Terrain\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Hallucinatory_Terrain\">Hallucinatory Terrain</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Massmorph\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Massmorph\">Massmorph</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Polymorph Others\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Polymorph_Others\">Polymorph Others</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Polymorph Self\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Polymorph_Self\">Polymorph Self</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Remove Curse (Curse)(MU)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Remove_Curse_(Curse)(MU)\">Remove Curse (Curse)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Wall of Fire\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Wall_of_Fire\">Wall of Fire</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Wall of Ice\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Wall_of_Ice\">Wall of Ice</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Wizard Eye\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Wizard_Eye\">Wizard Eye</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h2><span id=\"5th_Level\" class=\"mw-headline\">5th Level</span></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Animate Dead\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Animate_Dead\">Animate Dead</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Cloudkill\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Cloudkill\">Cloudkill</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Conjure Elemental\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Conjure_Elemental\">Conjure Elemental</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Contact Higher Plane\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Contact_Higher_P